menu "MegaWiFi options"

config MW_HTTP_USE_ESP
	bool "Use esp_http_client (HTTPS-capable)"
	default n
	help
	  If enabled, the firmware uses ESP-IDF's esp_http_client (supports HTTPS).
	  If disabled (default), a minimal plain-HTTP socket client is used to
	  avoid the esp_http_client transport issues seen on some firmware builds.

config MW_AUDIO_ENABLE
	bool "Enable PWM audio subsystem"
	default n
	help
	  If enabled, builds the audio component (Helix MP3 decoder, PWM driver,
	  ring buffer player) and embeds the test MP3 in flash. Disable to save
	  ~1.8 MB of flash and reduce binary size. Requires hardware cap mod
	  (C16/C17 → 10-22nF) for acceptable audio quality.

endmenu
